i-language:EN-US;mso-fareast-language:ZH-CN;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;\" lang=\"EN-US\">37</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5pt;mso-ascii-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';mso-hansi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0pt;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';mso-ansi-language:EN-US;mso-fareast-language:ZH-CN;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA;\">毫升，</span><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0pt;mso-ansi-language:EN-US;mso-fareast-language:ZH-CN;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;\" lang=\"EN-US\">1.25</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5pt;mso-ascii-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';mso-hansi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0pt;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';mso-ansi-language:EN-US;mso-fareast-language:ZH-CN;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA;\">盎司。没有其他样式。</span><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0pt;mso-ansi-language:EN-US;mso-fareast-language:ZH-CN;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;\" lang=\"EN-US\"><br />6.</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5pt;mso-ascii-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';mso-hansi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0pt;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';mso-ansi-language:EN-US;mso-fareast-language:ZH-CN;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA;\">安可来福是发明专利，根本不存在什么升级产品</span></span></p><br>符合安可来福（大连）生物科技有限公司代理商要求的客户可以直接留言与厂家联系。');
INSERT INTO `destoon_sell_data_5` VALUES('4489','诺丽果酵素饮招商 是由中国保健食品招商网会员发布的增强免疫力类招商信息：<br><p style=\"margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:red;font-size:12pt;mso-ascii-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;\">产品说明：</span><span style=\"color:red;font-size:12pt;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;mso-hansi-font-family:宋体;\" lang=\"EN-US\"></span></p><p style=\"margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;\" class=\"MsoPlainText\"><span style=\"color:red;font-size:12pt;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;mso-hansi-font-family:宋体;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">提高体力，增强细胞活性（天热时，细胞供氧及活性降低就会使人感觉乏力），延缓衰老，清除自由基。<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></span></p><p style=\"margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:red;font-size:12pt;mso-ascii-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;\">提高细胞携氧能力，改善微循环，改善头晕及脑供血不足；促进血脂、尿酸及血液中毒素的分解，降低血栓风险。</span><span style=\"color:red;font-size:12pt;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;mso-hansi-font-family:宋体;\" lang=\"EN-US\"></span></p><p style=\"margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;\" class=\"MsoPlainText\"><span style=\"color:red;font-size:12pt;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;mso-hansi-font-family:宋体;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">加快酒精分解排除，保护肝脏，减轻酒后头痛、头晕及肝区不适。<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></span></p><p style=\"margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;\" class=\"MsoPlainText\"><span style=\"color:red;font-size:12pt;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;mso-hansi-font-family:宋体;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">促进消化吸收，偏瘦人群可饭后补充酵素，维持体重人群可饭前补充酵素。<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></span></p><p style=\"margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:red;font-size:12pt;mso-ascii-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;\">酵素净血排毒可淡化色斑、改善肤质，抗氧化可延缓衰老等。</span><span style=\"color:red;font-size:12pt;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;mso-hansi-font-family:宋体;\" lang=\"EN-US\"></span></p><p style=\"margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;\" class=\"MsoPlainText\"><span style=\"color:red;font-size:12pt;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;mso-hansi-font-family:宋体;\"