tom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'黑体\';mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\"></span></p><p class=\"p0\" style=\"margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-weight:bold;font-size:10.5pt;color:#00823b;font-family:\'黑体\';mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\">商品介绍</span><span style=\"font-weight:bold;font-size:10.5pt;color:#00823b;font-family:\'黑体\';mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\">&nbsp;Introduction</span><span style=\"font-weight:bold;font-size:10.5pt;color:#00823b;font-family:\'黑体\';mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\"></span></p><p class=\"p0\" style=\"margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'黑体\';mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\"></span></p><p class=\"p0\" style=\"margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;text-indent:21pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'黑体\';mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\">蘑菇是真菌类的植，世界的食用蘑菇估计有</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'黑体\';mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\">2000</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'黑体\';mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\">，中有医疗价值的蘑菇大约为</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'黑体\';mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\">700</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'黑体\';mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\">种。在不同品种的蘑菇，致都含有维生素</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'黑体\';mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\">b1</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'黑体\';mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\">、维生素</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'黑体\';mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\">&nbsp;b2</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'黑体\';mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\">、烟酸、泛酸和维生素</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'黑体\';mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\">h</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'黑体\';mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\">。蘑菇多糖是蘑菇里重要的生物活性成，有很强的调节免疫功能的作，增强抗菌和抗病毒感染的能力。不仅如，菇还是一</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'黑体\';mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'黑体\';mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\">种含碘丰富的食品。</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'黑体\';mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'黑体\';mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\">食物里缺少碘会引起甲状腺肿，，国在食用盐里强制添加碘酸钾。多吃盐会损伤血，，吃盐又有可能引起碘缺乏。因，了补碘可多吃些蘑菇、葵花子和虾等含碘丰富的食物。</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'黑体\';mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\"></span></p><p class=\"p0\" style=\"margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-weight:bold;font-size:10.5pt;color:#00823b;font-family:\'黑体\';mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\"></span></p><p class=\"p0\" style=\"margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-weight:bold;font-size:10.5pt;color:#00823b;font-family:\'黑体\';mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\">商品展示</span><span style=\"font-weight:bold;font-size:10.5pt;color:#00823b;font-family:\'黑体\';mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\">&nbsp;Products&nbsp;show</span><span style=\"font-weight:bold;font-size:10.5pt;color:#00823b;font-family:\'黑体\';mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\"></span></p><p class=\"p0\" style=\"margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'黑体\';mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\"></span></p><p class=\"p0\" style=\"margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'黑体\';mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'黑体\';mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\">姬松茸称为巴西蘑菇、松茸菇、巴氏蘑菇、抗癌松茸等，隶属于真菌门，担子菌亚门、蘑菇目、蘑菇科、蘑菇属。该菌原产于北美南部和巴西、秘鲁等地的草场上，</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'黑体\';mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\">1956</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'黑体\';mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\">古本隆夫在巴西采集野生种进行组织分离，栽培试验和推广应用，因其原始种取自巴西，所以商品名拟称巴西蘑菇。</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'黑体\';mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\">1992</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'黑体\';mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\">年福建农科院从日本引进该菌种，经多点示范栽培，目前已在各地逐渐推广。姬松茸是珍稀菇类佳品，脆嫩滑爽，美味可口，营养成分较高，蛋白质与糖类是香菇的两倍，其菌蕾肥厚，菌柄肥整，以其浓味，可口鲜甜，倍受国内外消费者喜欢，成为宴席汤料不可缺少的上乘佳品。此外，姬松茸在增强的人体免疫力方面在食用菌中居于首位。</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'黑体\';mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\"></span></p><p class=\"p0\" style=\"margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'黑体\';mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\">温水浸泡发透备用。每次可将约</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'黑体\';mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\">6</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'黑体\';mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\">克干姬松茸（整菇）加入肉类烹饪、炖煮，香脆异常，口感绝佳。炖至汤汁变浓，作为食补，抗癌有极佳效果，也可以将该姬松茸取用</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'黑体\';mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\">6</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'黑体\';mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\">克左右，也可以像泡茶一样，每天饮用，具有抗癌效用。</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'黑体\';mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\"></span></p><p class=\"p0\" style=\"margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'黑体\';mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\"></span></p><p class=\"p0\" style=\"margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-weight:bold;font-size:10.5pt;color:#00823b;font-family:\'黑体\';mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\">商品价值</span><span style=\"font-weight:bold;font-size:10.5pt;color:#00823b;font-family:\'黑体\';mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\">&nbsp;Product&nbsp;value</span><span style=\"font-weight:bold;font-size:10.5pt;color:#00823b;font-family:\'黑体\';mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\"></span></p><p class=\"p0\" style=\"margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'黑体\';mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\"></span></p><p class=\"p0\" style=\"margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'黑体\';mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\">【本草详解】</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'黑体\';mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\"></span></p><p class=\"p0\" style=\"margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'黑体\';mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\">　　中医认为，姬松茸具有健脑、消炎、益肾、降血糖、改善糖尿病、降胆固醇、改善动脉硬化等功效。可抑制肿瘤</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'黑体\';mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\">(</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'黑体\';mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\">尤其是腹水癌</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'黑体\';mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\">)</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'黑体\';mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\">、医疗痔瘘、增强精力、防治心血管病。</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'黑体\';mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\"></span></p><p class=\"p0\" style=\"margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'黑体\';mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\">【养生必读】</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'黑体\';mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\"></span></p><p class=\"p0\" style=\"margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'黑体\';mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\">1</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'黑体\';mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\">、姬松茸的主要成分是多糖类和甾醇类，经热水提取的姬松茸β葡聚糖有较强的抗癌活性，有对人体增强精力的功效，并能抑制肿瘤细胞的生长，具有抗肿瘤作用，对致癌物质有吸收、排泄作用。</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'黑体\';mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\"></span></p><p class=\"p0\" style=\"margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'黑体\';mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\">2</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'黑体\';mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\">、姬松茸菌丝体粉中蛋白质含量达</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'黑体\';mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\">16-17%</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'黑体\';mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\">，这种是一种能杀死癌细胞的蛋白质，体粉中还含有人体必需的全部氨基酸。</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'黑体\';mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\"></span></p><p class=\"p0\" style=\"margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'黑体\';mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\">3</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'黑体\';mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\">、姬松茸含有具备抗瘤活性的“松茸多糖”，这是其他植物都没有的特殊双链生物活性物质，它具有超强抗基因突变能力和强抗癌作用，可破坏肿瘤细胞的遗传基因，从而达到抗基因突变，抑制肿瘤和控制肿瘤复发、转移的目的。</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'黑体\';mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\"></span></p><p class=\"p0\" style=\"margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'黑体\';mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\">4</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'黑体\';mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\">、姬松茸可促进人的骨髓的造血功能。</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'黑体\';mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\"></span></p><p class=\"p0\" style=\"margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'黑体\';mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\">5</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'黑体\';mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\">、姬松茸对干扰白血病的细胞增殖有抑制作用。生理活性多糖，适于治疗儿童白血病。</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'黑体\';mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\"></span></p><p class=\"p0\" style=\"margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'黑体\';mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\">6</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'黑体\';mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\">、姬松茸对肝、肾有保护作用，可长期服用。</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'黑体\';mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\"></span></p><p class=\"p0\" style=\"margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'黑体\';mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\"></span></p><p class=\"p0\" style=\"margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-weight:bold;font-size:10.5pt;color:#c00000;font-family:\'宋体\';mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\">公司地址：成都市高新西区天宇路</span><span style=\"font-weight:bold;font-size:10.5pt;color:#c00000;font-family:\'Calibri\';mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\">2</span><span style=\"font-weight:bold;font-size:10.5pt;color:#c00000;font-family:\'宋体\';mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\">号</span><span style=\"font-weight:bold;font-size:10.5pt;color:#c00000;font-family:\'Calibri\';mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\">.</span><span style=\"font-weight:bold;font-size:10.5pt;color:#c00000;font-family:\'宋体\';mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\">天府创意产业园</span><span style=\"font-weight:bold;font-size:10.5pt;color:#c00000;font-family:\'Calibri\';mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\">13</span><span style=\"font-weight:bold;font-size:10.5pt;color:#c00000;font-family:\'宋体\';mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\">栋</span></p><br>符合四川川岭苁珍食品有限公司代理商要求的客户可以直接留言与厂家联系。');
INSERT INTO `destoon_sell_data_5` VALUES('4660','中航人宇航果蔬餐招商 是由中国保健食品招商网会员发布的促进生长发育类招商信息：<br>&nbsp; \n宇航果蔬餐（快乐长高爱吃菜）\n宇航果蔬餐（快乐长高爱吃菜）依照《中国居民膳食营养素参考摄入量》要求，根据中国传统营养食疗理论，运用现代生物提取技术，精心选择天然绿色蔬菜水果、膳食纤维、豆奶粉等天然营养原料，经科学配伍，精制而成，天然绿色，营养全面，实为人们强身健体之佳品。\n主要原料：菠菜粉、芹菜粉、山楂粉、胡萝卜粉、豆奶粉、麦芽糊精、植脂末、木糖醇\n主要作用：\n1、健胃助消化，促进青少年身体的正常发育。\n2、调节新陈代谢，提高青少年的机体免疫力。\n3、具有补充钙、铁以及维生素C的良好功效。\n4、增智补脑，提高记忆力。\n5、促进青少年骨骼及牙齿的生长发育。<br>符合沈阳中航人航天高科技研发推广中心代理商要求的客户可以直接留言与厂家联系。');
