INSERT INTO `destoon_sell_data_5` VALUES('4689','神奇蓝水最前沿、最尖端招商 是由中国保健食品招商网会员发布的促进生长发育类招商信息：<br><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center;line-height:16.5pt;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt;font-family:方正大黑简体;background-color:white;background-position:initial initial;background-repeat:initial initial;\">神奇蓝水最前沿、最尖端<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center;line-height:16.5pt;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12pt;font-family:方正大黑简体;background-color:white;background-position:initial initial;background-repeat:initial initial;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center;line-height:16.5pt;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt;font-family:方正大黑简体;background-color:white;background-position:initial initial;background-repeat:initial initial;\">它是目前世界上最前沿、最尖端的细胞能量补充与抗氧化应激产品</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;color:#656565;background:white;mso-font-kerning:0pt;\"></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"text-indent:21pt;line-height:16.5pt;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12pt;background-color:white;background-position:initial initial;background-repeat:initial initial;\">Currentlythe world\'s most advanced, most sophisticated cellular energy supplement andanti-oxidation products</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;color:#656565;background:white;mso-font-kerning:0pt;\"></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;color:#333333;background:white;mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">&nbsp;</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:17.95pt;mso-para-margin-left:1.71gd;text-indent:23.6pt;mso-char-indent-count:1.96;text-autospace:ideograph-other;\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;color:#333333;background:white;mso-font-kerning:0pt;\">活性细胞能量液—神奇蓝水Ⅱ号（超强抗氧化剂）</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;color:#333333;background:white;mso-font-kerning:0pt;mso-bidi-font-weight:bold;\">主要成分是从千年古代腐殖植物种提取的富里酸（黄腐酸）</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">（</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Fulvic Acids</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">，代号</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">FA</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times Newroman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">）主要是一类含活性官能团的大分子芳香</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">-</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">脂肪族羟基羧酸的复杂混合物。</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:17.95pt;mso-para-margin-left:1.71gd;text-indent:20.6pt;mso-char-indent-count:1.96;text-autospace:ideograph-other;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">人类至少需要</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">90</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">种营养素才能保持健康。这些营养素包括至少</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">70</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">种矿物质，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">18</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">种氨基酸和三种基本脂肪酸。因此我们需要额外的物质帮助身体获得需要的营养。</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:18.0pt;text-indent:0cm;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1;tab-stops:36.0pt;text-autospace:ideograph-other;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family:Symbol;mso-fareast-font-family:Symbol;mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol\">·<span style=\"font-size:7pt;line-height:normal;font-family:\'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family: &quot;Times Newroman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">如果你现在正在使用离子或胶体标记的矿物质补充品，就有必要了解黄腐酸的作用。科学家发现黄腐酸是一种有助于营养吸收，并对困扰人类疾病和健康问题有积极影响的元素，他们甚至还把它称为仙丹！</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:18.0pt;text-indent:0cm;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1;tab-stops:36.0pt;text-autospace:ideograph-other;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family:Symbol;mso-fareast-font-family:Symbol;mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol\">·<span style=\"font-size:7pt;line-height:normal;font-family:\'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;color:#333333;background:white;mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">“神奇蓝水”</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">包含</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">70</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">多种重要矿物质。当矿物质接触到黄腐酸，以水为介质可以让它们自然溶解成离子形式。这些矿物质自然形成黄酸的一部分，变得有机和具有生物活性。因此，当矿物质通过涉及黄腐酸和光合作用的自然化学过程转变为有机体时，对人类和动物是安全的。</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:18.0pt;text-indent:0cm;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1;tab-stops:36.0pt;text-autospace:ideograph-other;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family:Symbol;mso-fareast-font-family:Symbol;mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol\">·<span style=\"font-size:7pt;line-height:normal;font-family:\'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family: &quot;Times Newroman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">具有解毒能力，可以清除人体内除草剂和杀虫剂等有毒物质，这是因为“</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;color:#333333;background:white;mso-font-kerning:0pt;\">神奇蓝水”</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times Newroman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">可以与许多放射性元素互动。因此，黄酸可以作为保护剂减少毒素对人体的损害。</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:18.0pt;text-indent:0cm;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1;tab-stops:36.0pt;text-autospace:ideograph-other;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family:Symbol;mso-fareast-font-family:Symbol;mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol\">·<span style=\"font-size:7pt;line-height:normal;font-family:\'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family: &quot;Times Newroman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">活性细胞能量素“</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;color:#333333;background:white;mso-font-kerning:0pt;\">神奇蓝水”</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times Newroman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">可以激活消化酶。在我们吃东西的时候，身体会运行一系列复杂活动，旨在消化摄入的食物。然后把这些食物消化转换为能量。如果没有消化酶参与，食物就难以处理，并会腐烂在胃里，甚至最终导致死亡。</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:18.0pt;text-indent:0cm;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1;tab-stops:36.0pt;text-autospace:ideograph-other;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family:Symbol;mso-fareast-font-family:Symbol;mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol\">·<span style=\"font-size:7pt;line-height:normal;font-family:\'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family: &quot;Times Newroman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">有降低自由基氧化作用的作用，因为黄腐酸是一种非常强大的抗氧化剂。众所周知，有害自由基可以散布到全身，造成组织损害和基因改变。</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:18.0pt;text-indent:0cm;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1;tab-stops:36.0pt;text-autospace:ideograph-other;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family:Symbol;mso-fareast-font-family:Symbol;mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol\">·<span style=\"font-size:7pt;line-height:normal;font-family:\'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family: &quot;Times Newroman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">能够有效压制和排除包括重金属和污染物在内的各种有毒物质。此外，它还负责把必需营养素带进细胞。已证明黄酸可以把天然毒素和螯合剂降低到无害状态。</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:18.0pt;text-indent:0cm;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1;tab-stops:36.0pt;text-autospace:ideograph-other;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family:Symbol;mso-fareast-font-family:Symbol;mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol\">·<span style=\"font-size:7pt;line-height:normal;font-family:\'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family: &quot;Times Newroman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">有报告说黄腐酸还有舒缓氧气不足和增加细胞活性的作用。</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:7.5pt;margin-left:18.0pt;text-indent:0cm;line-height:16.5pt;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1;tab-stops:36.0pt;background:#FFFCF6;mso-shading:windowtext;mso-pattern:solid #FFFCF6;text-autospace:ideograph-other;vertical-align:middle;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family:Symbol;mso-fareast-font-family:Symbol;mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol\">·<span style=\"font-size:7pt;line-height:normal;font-family:\'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family: &quot;Times Newroman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">已被证明是一种性质上最强大的有机电解质。所有细胞都有电能，当细胞电能减少时，就会感觉疲软，疾病随时可能发生。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family:Arial;background-position:initial initial;background-repeat:initial initial;\"></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:20.6pt;mso-char-indent-count:1.96;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">“神奇蓝水”正是由美国生命科学研究院研发生产，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">e</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">家通国际养生机构最先引进国内的一款世界顶级高端产品。</span></p><br>符合北京市普中康泰国际商贸有限公司代理商要求的客户可以直接留言与厂家联系。');
