INSERT INTO `destoon_sell_data_5` VALUES('4691','Maca（玛卡）招商 是由中国保健食品招商网会员发布的增强免疫力类招商信息：<br><P style=\"LINE-HEIGHT: 14pt; TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt\" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: black; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-themecolor: text1\" lang=EN-US>Maca</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: black; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-themecolor: text1\">（玛卡）</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-fareast\">是一种植物，学名是</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: \'Franklin Gothic Medium\',\'sans-serif\'\" lang=EN-US>Lepidium Meye Niiwaop</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-fareast\">，原产于秘鲁中部基宁及帕斯科附近海拔<SPAN lang=EN-US>4000</SPAN>米以上的安第斯山和中国云南西北部海拔<SPAN lang=EN-US>3500</SPAN>米以上山区，色泽黄中带紫，类似萝卜，是高原唯一的十字花</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri\">植物。</SPAN></P>\n<P><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-themecolor: text1; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-bidi-theme-font: minor-bidi; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA\">由于现代生活的节奏加快，人们每天都要穿梭在各种场合，回到家里要应对家里的大大小小的事务，长期以往，人们的疲劳感会越来越严重，身体也会日渐衰弱，因免疫力下降而引起的各种各样的病症，这都是恶性循环的场景。我们期盼着幸福美满的家庭、事业有成的工作、亲朋好友的健康，想要实现这样的夙愿唯一要保证的就是每天都有着充沛的精神，充满能量的体魄，无论任何事情发生都有办法去应对，为了完成人们的急需，我公司发现了在高原<SPAN lang=EN-US>3500</SPAN>米以上的地方有一种叫<SPAN lang=EN-US>maca</SPAN>（玛卡）的植物，从<SPAN lang=EN-US>1994</SPAN>年</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-themecolor: text1; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">意大利科学家<SPAN lang=EN-US>Dini</SPAN></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-themecolor: text1; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-bidi-theme-font: minor-bidi; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA\">发现玛卡中富含</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-themecolor: text1; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">数百种的营养的维生素，到<SPAN lang=EN-US>1999</SPAN>年美国科学家发现玛咖酰胺（<SPAN lang=EN-US>macamides</SPAN>）和玛咖稀（<SPAN lang=EN-US>macaenes</SPAN>）这两种新的植物活性成分，<SPAN lang=EN-US>maca</SPAN>（玛卡）给很多的科学家带来很多研究的课题，我国中央电视台新闻<SPAN lang=EN-US>30</SPAN>分报道了<SPAN lang=EN-US>maca</SPAN>提高肾动力的对比发现。</SPAN></P><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-themecolor: text1; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\"><SPAN lang=EN-U