INSERT INTO `destoon_sell_data_5` VALUES('4834','硒虫草大豆异黄酮片招商 是由中国保健食品招商网会员发布的延缓衰老类招商信息：<br><p class=\"p0\" style=\"margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-size:12.0000pt;font-family:\'宋体\';\">总所周知“虫草、人参、鹿茸”被誉为中国中药三宝，但不是所有的虫草都叫硒虫草！当</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-size:12.0000pt;font-family:\'Calibri\';\">虫草真菌</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-size:12.0000pt;font-family:\'宋体\';\">与</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-size:12.0000pt;font-family:\'Calibri\';\">蝙蝠蛾幼虫</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-size:12.0000pt;font-family:\'宋体\';\">的结合，缔造了独特的冬虫夏草；而硒与冬虫夏草的完美碰撞，便成就了绝无仅有的硒虫草。</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-size:12.0000pt;font-family:\'Calibri\';\">硒元素是人体必需的常量矿物质营养素。硒遍布各组织器官和体液，肾中浓度最高，对提高免疫力和预防癌症非常重要。由于人体内硒不存在长期贮藏硒的器官，机体所需的硒应该不断从饮食中得到足够量的硒，硒浓度的平衡对许多器官、组织的生理功能有着重要的保护作用和促进作用</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-size:12.0000pt;font-family:\'宋体\';\">。硒虫草产品产自自享有“世界硒都”美誉的湖北恩施境内，是由中科院微生物研究所与湖北圣峰药业有限公司共同利用恩施丰富的天然硒资源经多年研究而培育出的富硒冬虫夏草，将虫草的功效和硒的作用有机结合为一体，让优质的冬虫夏草基因在产品中得到了完美表达。实验研究表明硒虫草除具有天然虫草的营养成分和药理作用外，还含有丰富的硒酸脂多糖、硒<span style=\"font-family:Calibri;\">-</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">代蛋氨酸和硒</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri;\">-</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">代胱氨酸等有机硒化合物，具有抗癌防癌、增强免疫力、抗衰老和强壮滋补等优于天然虫草和其它人工培育虫草的独特功效，堪称“硒世珍宝”，是人们日常补硒、养生、滋补之珍品。</span></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-size:12.0000pt;font-family:\'宋体\';\"></span></p><p class=\"p0\" style=\"margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-size:12.0000pt;font-family:\'宋体\';\">&nbsp;</span></p><p class=\"p0\" style=\"margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-weight:bold;font-size:12.0000pt;font-family:\'宋体\';\">大豆异黄酮，焕发年轻态新巢！</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-weight:bold;font-size:12.0000pt;font-family:\'宋体\';\"></span></p><p class=\"p15\" style=\"margin-bottom:13.4500pt;margin-top:13.4500pt;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-size:12.0000pt;font-family:\'宋体\';\">卵巢是女性的秘密花园，在学术界更有卵巢老</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-size:12.0000pt;font-family:\'Calibri\';\">1</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-size:12.0000pt;font-family:\'宋体\';\">岁，女人老</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-size:12.0000pt;font-family:\'Calibri\';\">10</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-size:12.0000pt;font-family:\'宋体\';\">岁的说法。女人们抱怨自己的内分泌不好，<span style=\"font-family:Calibri;\">90%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">以上的女性却从不知晓内分泌的根源在于卵巢。</span></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-size:12.0000pt;font-family:\'宋体\';\">大豆异黄酮</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-size:12.0000pt;font-family:\'Calibri\';\">是从植物中提取，与</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-size:12.0000pt;font-family:\'Calibri\';\">雌激素</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-size:12.0000pt;font-family:\'Calibri\';\">有相似结构，因此大豆异黄酮又称</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-size:12.0000pt;font-family:\'Calibri\';\">植物雌激素</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-size:12.0000pt;font-family:\'宋体\';\">，通过微循环靶向抵达卵巢，</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-size:12.0000pt;font-family:\'Calibri\';\">能够弥补<span style=\"font-family:Calibri;\">30</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">岁以后女性</span></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-size:12.0000pt;font-family:\'Calibri\';\">雌性激素</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-size:12.0000pt;font-family:\'Calibri\';\">分泌不足的缺陷，改善皮肤水分及弹性状况，缓解</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-size:12.0000pt;font-family:\'Calibri\';\">更年期</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-size:12.0000pt;font-family:\'Calibri\';\">综合症和改善</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-size:12.0000pt;font-family:\'Calibri\';\">骨质疏松</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-size:12.0000pt;font-family:\'Calibri\';\">，使女性再现青春魅力。</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-size:12.0000pt;font-family:\'Calibri\';\">大豆异黄酮</span