font-family:\'Times New Roman\';\">100%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">纯胶原蛋白，效果提升</span><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';\">90%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">以上。</span></span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\';mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\"></span></p><p class=\"p0\" style=\"margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-weight:bold;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\">迪娜丽姿纳胶原蛋白原液的功效</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-weight:bold;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\"></span></p><p class=\"p0\" style=\"margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-weight:bold;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\">美白　多途径抑制黑色素</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-weight:bold;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\"></span></p><p class=\"p0\" style=\"margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\';mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\">抑制皮肤黑色素生成的方法有两种，一种是避免紫外线到达皮肤内部的防晒法，另一种则是抑制黑色素生成，既避免黑色素生成细胞制造出黑色素。迪娜丽姿胶原蛋白原液全方面抑制黑色素的形成，原理如下：</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\';mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\"></span></p><p class=\"p0\" style=\"margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\';mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\">第一、迪娜丽姿胶原蛋白原液中的独特成分能有效吸收照射到皮肤内部的紫外线，减少紫外线对黑色素细胞的刺激<span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">从根本上抑制或减少黑色素的形成，防止黑色素沉积。第二，迪娜丽姿胶原蛋白原液能使细胞粘接更紧密，新生细胞速度加快，不给黑色素、毒素聚集藏身之地，全面抑制黑色素的产生，达到彻底美白的目的。</span></span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\';mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\"></span></p><p class=\"p0\" style=\"margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-weight:bold;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\">抗衰　补充精纯胶原蛋白，去皱紧肤</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-weight:bold;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\"></span></p><p class=\"p0\" style=\"margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\';mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\">人之所以会老化、体力衰退、皮肤失去光泽及弹性，除了年龄是无法抗拒的因素外，胶原蛋白之现代医学家研究断言：<span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';\">“</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">皮肤衰老过程，就是胶原蛋白流失的过程。迪娜丽姿胶原蛋白原液中独有的活性小分子进入真皮组织后，能迅速填补局部塌陷，恢复皮肤细胞活性，激活皮肤内部弹力胶原的生成，维持细胞矩阵结构并修复皮肤内部的矩阵结构，从而改善松弛，收紧皮肤，减少深皱纹、平复细纹、眼袋等，延缓皮肤衰老，让皮肤重现年轻时的精致，逆转衰老的过程。</span></span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\';mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\"></span></p><p class=\"p0\" style=\"margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-weight:bold;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\">修复　恢复细胞功能，增进细胞活力</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-weight:bold;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\"></span></p><p class=\"p0\" style=\"margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\';mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\">当皮肤细胞的细胞膜变厚，细胞膜的渗透性就会降低，于是便限制了细胞营养的供应。迪娜丽姿胶原蛋白原液，能够渗入<span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';\">A.R.I</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">的老化触发区，让细胞壁保持年轻状态，让细胞的营养交换不断增加。恢复因紫外辐射、抽烟、饮食等引进的细胞通信障碍问题，而细胞间的通信恰是激活胶原蛋白，维持细胞矩阵结构的关键因素。</span></span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\';mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\"></span></p><p class=\"p0\" style=\"margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-weight:bold;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\">祛斑　加速新陈代谢，促死皮脱落</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-weight:bold;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\"></span></p><p class=\"p0\" style=\"margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\';mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\">斑点的形成最根本的原因往往是黑色素的沉积或者某些有害物质对皮肤内部造成的伤害在皮肤表面的显现，一旦形成，即表明皮肤内部结构遭受了损坏，这时从皮肤表面的治疗几乎没有任何收效，而治本的关键必须从调节皮肤内循环着手。迪娜丽姿胶原蛋白原液通过对皮肤各功能的修复，让皮肤的各组织处在相当优秀的运行环境下，补充皮肤新陈代谢所需要的关键物质，加快代谢速度，缩短皮肤代谢周期，促进角质层的迅速正常脱落，去掉死皮，长出新的皮肤层，从而淡化已经形成的色斑，最终彻底祛除色斑。</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\';mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\"></span></p><p class=\"p0\" style=\"margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-weight:bold;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\">保湿　收缩毛孔，提升锁水能</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'宋体\';font-weight:bold;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\">力</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-weight:bold;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\"></span></p><p class=\"p0\" style=\"margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\';mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\">健康的皮肤必须保证时刻水润光泽，水分对皮肤起保护作用的同时，也能让皮肤显得柔嫩清爽。皮脂膜是由皮脂、汗水及皮肤所蒸发的水分，一半水一半油脂所形成的酸性膜，存在于皮肤表面，可以保护皮肤免于外界环境的伤害，维持皮肤湿润。迪娜丽姿胶原蛋白原液中的独有的三螺旋结构，能强力锁住<span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';\">30</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">倍的水分，有效收缩毛孔，提高皮肤内皮脂膜的功能，提升真皮层的锁水能力，从而达到紧缩毛孔，持久保湿的效果。</span></span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\';mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\"></span></p><p class=\"p0\" style=\"margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\';mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\"></span></p><p class=\"p0\" style=\"margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-weight:bold;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\">迪娜丽姿</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'宋体\';font-weight:bold;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\">胶原蛋白</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-weight:bold;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\">原液使用周期的临床效果</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-weight:bold;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\"></span></p><p class=\"p0\" style=\"margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\';mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\">●<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">连续使用</span><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';\">10</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">天后&nbsp;您可以明显感受到皮肤变的柔软，湿润度增加、皮脂减少、皮肤不在再油腻，皮肤亮白度平均提高</span><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';\">2-6</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">度，比使用前略白，触摸时明显感觉细嫩。</span></span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\';mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\"></span></p><p class=\"p0\" style=\"margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\';mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\">●<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">连续使用</span><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';\">25</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">天后&nbsp;脸上细纹边舒展，皮肤变的更有水嫩，色斑、痘印、皱纹开始淡化，皮肤锁水能力加强，皮肤亮白度平均提高</span><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';\">4-12</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">度，肌肤紧致，有弹性。</span></span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\';mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\"></span></p><p class=\"p0\" style=\"margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\';mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\">●<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">连续使用</span><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';\">40</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">天后&nbsp;您的皮肤在不知不觉中轻松恢复到了年轻时的细腻、紧致，细纹、眼袋、黑斑、痘印基本消失，皮肤抵抗外界刺激性的能力和自我恢复能力显著加强。</span></span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\';mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\"></span></p><p class=\"p0\" style=\"margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\';mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\">迪娜丽姿胶原蛋白原液适合人群</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\';mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\"></span></p><p class=\"p0\" style=\"margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\';mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\">1<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">、由于工作劳累，睡眠不足形成的皮肤晦暗无光、发黄、皮肤弹性差等皮肤衰老的不良症状。</span></span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\';mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\"></span></p><p class=\"p0\" style=\"margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\';mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\">2<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">、由于年龄、太阳辐射因素引起的皮肤松弛、下垂、皱纹、干燥等皮肤衰老现象。</span></span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\';mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\"></span></p><p class=\"p0\" style=\"margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\';mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\">3<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">、由于体内异常黑色素分泌旺盛，大量沉积皮肤表面，肌肤不能及时代谢出异常黑色素，形成各种色斑，如色斑、黄褐斑、雀斑、早期老年斑等。</span></span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\';mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\"></span></p><p class=\"p0\" style=\"margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\';mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\"></span></p><br>符合康滢生物科技有限公司（广州分公司）代理商要求的客户可以直接留言与厂家联系。');
