INSERT INTO `destoon_sell_data_5` VALUES('4874','畅精灵晶钻海藻冻招商 是由中国保健食品招商网会员发布的改善胃肠类招商信息：<br><p><span style=\"color:black;font-size:10.5pt;mso-ascii-font-family:Tahoma;mso-hansi-font-family:Tahoma;mso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 医学研究证明宿便是危害人体健康美容的罪魁祸首，医学把宿便称为是体内的毒瘤，每天都在分泌出大量的毒素，宿便没有及时的排出就像（食品</span></span><span style=\"font-family:\'Tahoma\',\'sans-serif\';color:black;font-size:10.5pt;\" lang=\"EN-US\">-</span><span style=\"color:black;font-size:10.5pt;mso-ascii-font-family:Tahoma;mso-hansi-font-family:Tahoma;mso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">垃圾</span></span><span style=\"font-family:\'Tahoma\',\'sans-serif\';color:black;font-size:10.5pt;\" lang=\"EN-US\">-</span><span style=\"color:black;font-size:10.5pt;mso-ascii-font-family:Tahoma;mso-hansi-font-family:Tahoma;mso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">发酵</span></span><span style=\"font-family:\'Tahoma\',\'sans-serif\';color:black;font-size:10.5pt;\" lang=\"EN-US\">-</span><span style=\"color:black;font-size:10.5pt;mso-ascii-font-family:Tahoma;mso-hansi-font-family:Tahoma;mso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">毒垃圾在体内再次让肠道吸收），初期会导致脸上长斑长痘，口臭、脸色灰暗无光泽、肠道老化，无活力等症状，宿便长期堆积在肠道内严重会导致肠癌。我们人体正常排便是每天</span></span><span style=\"font-family:\'Tahoma\',\'sans-serif\';color:black;font-size:10.5pt;\" lang=\"EN-US\">1-2</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><span style=\"color:black;font-size:10.5pt;mso-ascii-font-family:Tahoma;mso-hansi-font-family:Tahoma;mso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;\">次，如果经常没有就会导致便秘，所以我们要及时的清肠排毒，把体内的宿便残渣毒素排出体外。</span><span style=\"font-family:\'Tahoma\',\'sans-serif\';color:black;font-size:10.5pt;\" lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:\'Tahoma\',\'sans-serif\';color:black;font-size:10.5pt;\" lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:yes;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><span style=\"color:black;font-size:10.5pt;mso-ascii-font-family:Tahoma;mso-hansi-font-family:Tahoma;mso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;\">台湾美是康生物科技经过多年的研究努力终于研发出系列绿色健康的排毒功能食品，只需要像吃零食一样就可以达到排毒养生的功效，倡导“体内环保“，做到绿色、健康、养生于一体。产品上市就受到台湾、日韩等欧美国家的热烈推崇，在海外印发一场健康排毒风暴，慢慢席卷全球。</span><span style=\"font-family:\'Tahoma\',\'sans-serif\';color:black;font-size:10.5pt;\" lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:\'Tahoma\',\'sans-serif\';color:black;font-size:10.5pt;\" lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:yes;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span style=\"color:black;font-size:10.5pt;mso-ascii-font-family:Tahoma;mso-hansi-font-family:Tahoma;mso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">“畅精灵晶钻海藻胶“以优质海藻胶为载体，融入魔芋粉、郁李仁、决明子、维生素</span></span><span style=\"font-family:\'Tahoma\',\'sans-serif\';color:black;font-size:10.5pt;\" lang=\"EN-US\">c</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><span style=\"color:black;font-size:10.5pt;mso-ascii-font-family:Tahoma;mso-hansi-font-family:Tahoma;mso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;\">等有益物质，能够促进肠胃蠕动，提高肠胃功能，改善便秘，抑制有害细菌的繁殖，减少肠道中内毒素以及致癌物的沉积。有效排出体内毒素、油腻，代谢体内多余脂肪，降低血糖血压胆固醇，具有养颜美容，除痘祛斑，减肥养生之功效。</span><span style=\"font-family:\'Tahoma\',\'sans-serif\';color:black;font-size:10.5pt;\" lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><span style=\"color:black;font-size:10.5pt;mso-ascii-font-family:Tahoma;mso-hansi-font-family:Tahoma;mso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;\">海藻胶：顾名思义就是海藻的提取物，从海藻中提取的多糖类胶质，具有保鲜和独特的保健功效。</span><span style=\"font-family:\'Tahoma\',\'sans-serif\';color:black;font-size:10.5pt;\" lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></p><p style=\"text-indent:-36pt;margin-left:36pt;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1;\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Tahoma\',\'sans-serif\';color:black;font-size:10.5pt;mso-fareast-font-family:Tahoma;\" lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"mso-list:Ignore;\">1、<span style=\"font:7pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><span style=\"color:black;font-size:10.5pt;mso-ascii-font-family:Tahoma;mso-hansi-font-family:Tahoma;mso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;\">增加肌肤的保水性，使肌肤的保湿效果增大，因而促使肌肤更显靓丽且不易产生过敏反应。</span><span style=\"font-family:\'Tahoma\',\'sans-serif\';color:black;font-size:10.5pt;\" lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></p><p style=\"text-indent:-36pt;margin-left:36pt;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1;\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Tahoma\',\'sans-serif\';color:black;font-size:10.5pt;mso-fareast-font-family:Tahoma;\" lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"mso-list:Ignore;\">2、<span style=\"font:7pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><span style=\"color:black;font-size:10.5pt;mso-ascii-font-family:Tahoma;mso-hansi-font-family:Tahoma;mso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;\">增加肌肤的紧缩性及弹性，使松弛的肌肤回复年轻状态，并可因此达到去除皱纹的目的。</span><span style=\"font-family:\'Tahoma\',\'sans-serif\';color:black;font-size:10.5pt;\" lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></p><p style=\"text-indent:-36pt;margin-left:36pt;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1;\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Tahoma\',\'sans-serif\';color:black;font-size:10.5pt;mso-fareast-font-family:Tahoma;\" lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"mso-list:Ignore;\">3、<span style=\"font:7pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><span style=\"color:black;font-size:10.5pt;mso-ascii-font-family:Tahoma;mso-hansi-font-family:Tahoma;mso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;\">帮助肌肤皮肤的功能，增加肌肤的免疫及保护作用。对暴晒、睡眠不足引起的黑斑有修复作用。</span><span style=\"font-family:\'Tahoma\',\'sans-serif\';color:black;font-size:10.5pt;\" lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></p><p style=\"text-indent:-36pt;margin-left:36pt;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1;\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Tahoma\',\'sans-serif\';color:black;font-size:10.5pt;mso-fareast-font-family:Tahoma;\" lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"mso-list:Ignore;\">4、<span style=\"font:7pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><span style=\"color:black;font-size:10.5pt;mso-ascii-font-family:Tahoma;mso-hansi-font-family:Tahoma;mso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;\">因其有的保水性及紧缩性的双重作用，可改善干性及油性肌肤的分泌状态，使之渐趋于中性肌肤，并促使毛细孔收缩细致。改善因电脑辐射、油脂分泌过剩造成的毛孔粗大。</span><span style=\"font-family:\'Tahoma\',\'sans-serif\';color:black;font-size:10.5pt;\" lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></p><p style=\"text-indent:-36pt;margin-left:36pt;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1;\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Tahoma\',\'sans-serif\';color:black;font-size:10.5pt;mso-fareast-font-family:Tahoma;\" lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"mso-list:Ignore;\">5、<span style=\"font:7pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><span style=\"color:black;font-size:10.5pt;mso-ascii-font-family:Tahoma;mso-hansi-font-family:Tahoma;mso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">适合油性</span></span><span style=\"font-family:\'Tahoma\',\'sans-serif\';color:black;font-size:10.5pt;\" lang=\"EN-US\">/</span><span style=\"color:black;font-size:10.5pt;mso-ascii-font-family:Tahoma;mso-hansi-font-family:Tahoma;mso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">暗疮</span></span><span style=\"font-family:\'Tahoma\',\'sans-serif\';color:black;font-size:10.5pt;\" lang=\"EN-US\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><span style=\"color:black;font-size:10.5pt;mso-ascii-font-family:Tahoma;mso-hansi-font-family:Tahoma;mso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;\">红肿皮肤，有平衡油脂分泌，消炎杀菌之功效，对暗疮有特别疗效。</span><span style=\"font-family:\'Tahoma\',\'sans-serif\';color:black;font-size:10.5pt;\" lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></p><p style=\"margin-left:36pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><span style=\"color:black;font-size:10.5pt;mso-ascii-font-family:Tahoma;mso-hansi-font-family:Tahoma;mso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;\">厦门强生堂将畅精灵排毒海藻胶带到中国大陆，。必将会引发大陆市场的火爆，排毒瘦身的理念必定会风靡全国。期待与您共创辉煌。</span><span style=\"font-family:\'Tahoma\',\'sans-serif\';color:black;font-size:10.5pt;\" lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><span style=\"color:black;font-size:10.5pt;mso-ascii-font-family:Tahoma;mso-hansi-font-family:Tahoma;mso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;\">（果冻装）产品自身卖点：</span><span style=\"font-family:\'Tahoma\',\'sans-serif\';color:black;font-size:10.5pt;\" lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></p><p style=\"text-indent:36.75pt;mso-char-indent-count:3.5;\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Tahoma\',\'sans-serif\';color:black;font-size:10.5pt;\" lang=\"EN-US\">1</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><span style=\"color:black;font-size:10.5pt;mso-ascii-font-family:Tahoma;mso-hansi-font-family:Tahoma;mso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;\">、海洋生物提取，萃取植物精华，纯天然绿色食品，不含任何有害成分。</span><span style=\"font-family:\'Tahoma\',\'sans-serif\';color:black;font-size:10.5pt;\" lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></p><p style=\"text-indent:36.75pt;mso-char-indent-count:3.5;\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Tahoma\',\'sans-serif\';color:black;font-size:10.5pt;\" lang=\"EN-US\">2</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><span style=\"color:black;font-size:10.5pt;mso-ascii-font-family:Tahoma;mso-hansi-font-family:Tahoma;mso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;\">、口感爽滑，酸甜可口。（天然海藻搭配水果浓汁，爽滑美味）</span><span style=\"font-family:\'Tahoma\',\'sans-serif\';color:black;font-size:10.5pt;\" lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></p><p style=\"text-indent:36.75pt;mso-char-indent-count:3.5;\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Tahoma\',\'sans-serif\';color:black;font-size:10.5pt;\" lang=\"EN-US\">3</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><span style=\"color:black;font-size:10.5pt;mso-ascii-font-family:Tahoma;mso-hansi-font-family:Tahoma;mso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;\">、携带方便，开袋即食。（单挑包装便于携带，果冻载体即开即食）</span><span style=\"font-family:\'Tahoma\',\'sans-serif\';color:black;font-size:10.5pt;\" lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></p><p style=\"text-indent:36.75pt;mso-char-indent-count:3.5;\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Tahoma\',\'sans-serif\';color:black;font-size:10.5pt;\" lang=\"EN-US\">4</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><span style=\"color:black;font-size:10.5pt;mso-ascii-font-family:Tahoma;mso-hansi-font-family:Tahoma;mso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;\">、台湾生产，品质保障。（采用台湾先进生产工艺，用料精选，严格把关）</span><span style=\"font-family:\'Tahoma\',\'sans-serif\';color:black;font-size:10.5pt;\" lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></p><p style=\"text-indent:36.75pt;mso-char-indent-count:3.5;\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Tahoma\',\'sans-serif\';color:black;font-size:10.5pt;\" lang=\"EN-US\">5</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><span style=\"color:black;font-size:10.5pt;mso-ascii-font-family:Tahoma;mso-hansi-font-family:Tahoma;mso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;\">、市场空白，竞争力强。（排毒类产品的市场上首次推出果冻载体的进口产品）</span><span style=\"font-family:\'Tahoma\',\'sans-serif\';color:black;font-size:10.5pt;\" lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></p><p style=\"text-indent:10.5pt;mso-char-indent-count:1.0;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><span style=\"color:black;font-size:10.5pt;mso-ascii-font-family:Tahoma;mso-hansi-font-family:Tahoma;mso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;\">市场前景：</span><span style=\"font-family:\'Tahoma\',\'sans-serif\';color:black;font-size:10.5pt;\" lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></p><p style=\"text-indent:36.75pt;mso-char-indent-count:3.5;\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Tahoma\',\'sans-serif\';color:black;font-size:10.5pt;\" lang=\"EN-US\">1</span><span style=\"color:black;font-size:10.5pt;mso-ascii-font-family:Tahoma;mso-hansi-font-family:Tahoma;mso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">、随着社会的发展国民经济收入的增加，国人越来越注重健康与保养。</span></span><span style=\"font-family:\'Tahoma\',\'sans-serif\';color:black;font-size:10.5pt;\" lang=\"EN-US\">2015</span><span style=\"color:black;font-size:10.5pt;mso-ascii-font-family:Tahoma;mso-hansi-font-family:Tahoma;mso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">年我过功能保健品销售额将达</span></span><span style=\"font-family:\'Tahoma\',\'sans-serif\';color:black;font-size:10.5pt;\" lang=\"EN-US\">4500</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><span style=\"color:black;font-size:10.5pt;mso-ascii-font-family:Tahoma;mso-hansi-font-family:Tahoma;mso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;\">亿</span><span style=\"font-family:\'Tahoma\',\'sans-serif\';color:black;font-size:10.5pt;\" lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></p><p style=\"text-indent:36.75pt;mso-char-indent-count:3.5;\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Tahoma\',\'sans-serif\';color:black;font-size:10.5pt;\" lang=\"EN-US\">2</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><span style=\"color:black;font-size:10.5pt;mso-ascii-font-family:Tahoma;mso-hansi-font-family:Tahoma;mso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;\">、激素、催生素、尾气、防腐剂、工业污染、空气污染、雾霾天气等，使雾霾的身体慢慢积累了大量的毒素，这些毒素在体内侵蚀着雾霾的健康。</span><span style=\"font-family:\'Tahoma\',\'sans-serif\';color:black;font-size:10.5pt;\" lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></p><p style=\"text-indent:36.75pt;mso-char-indent-count:3.5;\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Tahoma\',\'sans-serif\';color:black;font-size:10.5pt;\" lang=\"EN-US\">3</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><span style=\"color:black;font-size:10.5pt;mso-ascii-font-family:Tahoma;mso-hansi-font-family:Tahoma;mso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;\">、由于饮食不规律、熬夜等问题造成内分泌失调，代谢功能减退。饮食过于精细，膳食纤维不足，加上肠道内壁的褶皱是的体内残渣不能完全排除体外，堆积形成宿便导致便秘。</span><span style=\"font-family:\'Tahoma\',\'sans-serif\';color:black;font-size:10.5pt;\" lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></p><p style=\"margin-left:36pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Tahoma\',\'sans-serif\';color:black;font-size:10.5pt;\" lang=\"EN-US\">4</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><span style=\"color:black;font-size:10.5pt;mso-ascii-font-family:Tahoma;mso-hansi-font-family:Tahoma;mso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;\">、宿便产生的毒素被人体吸收后，会降低人体免疫力，诱发各种疾病。轻度导致面部长斑、长痘、脸色暗黄、口臭、痤疮、肥胖，重者引起肛肠疾病，结肠癌，形成粪便溃疡，诱发心脑血管疾病，影响大脑功能，导致女性痛经，男性性功能障碍等</span><span style=\"font-family:\'Tahoma\',\'sans-serif\';color:black;font-size:10.5pt;\" lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></p><p style=\"margin-left:36pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Tahoma\',\'sans-serif\';color:black;font-size:10.5pt;\" lang=\"EN-US\">5</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><span style=\"color:black;font-size:10.5pt;mso-ascii-font-family:Tahoma;mso-hansi-font-family:Tahoma;mso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;\">、国内市场上的排毒清肠产品大多是有添加泻药成分，排出的是体内水分，反而造成人体脱水拉肚子。本品是来自海洋生物发酵萃取植物精华，无添加任何有害成分，国际化标准生产，台湾原装进口，台湾嘉义大学生物研究所科研团队，品质保障。</span><span style=\"font-family:\'Tahoma\',\'sans-serif\';color:black;font-size:10.5pt;\" lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></p><p style=\"margin-left:36pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Tahoma\',\'sans-serif\';color:black;font-size:10.5pt;\" lang=\"EN-US\">6</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><span style=\"color:black;font-size:10.5pt;mso-ascii-font-family:Tahoma;mso-hansi-font-family:Tahoma;mso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;\">、台湾进口果冻型排毒果胶口感爽滑，效果显著，携带方便，市场竞争力强。</span><span style=\"font-family:\'Tahoma\',\'sans-serif\';color:black;font-size:10.5pt;\" lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></p><p style=\"text-indent:10.5pt;mso-char-indent-count:1.0;\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Tahoma\',\'sans-serif\';color:black;font-size:10.5pt;\" lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></p><br>符合厦门强生堂生物科技有限公司代理商要求的客户可以直接留言与厂家联系。');
INSERT INTO `destoon_sell_data_5` VALUES('4875','天保堂人参纯元粉 是由中国保健食品招商网会员发布的延缓衰老类招商信息：<br><p>人参纯元粉是香港天保堂新一代养生圣品，是运用国家科技部重点科研项目---“纯精元萃取技术”和国家重点保护专利----“低温高压差层析技术”为核心研发而成。</p><p>人参纯元粉经国家多家三甲医院和科研机构临床验证，具有以下疗效：</p><p>&nbsp;1.抗疲劳，快速恢复体力； </p><p>2.增强记忆力，促进大脑活力； </p><p>3.强身健元，促进性功能；</p><p>&nbsp;4.增强心肌活力，改善心脏功能； </p><p>5.降血糖血脂，促进血糖和血脂平稳； </p><p>6.增强机体免疫能力，延年益寿； </p><p>7.抗肿瘤作用，抑制肿瘤再生； </p><p>8.延缓机体衰老，抗氧化和抗自由基作用。 </p><br>符合中山天保参茸有限公司代理商要求的客户可以直接留言与厂家联系。');
INSERT INTO `destoon_sell_data_5` VALUES('4876','猴头菇高钙复合固体饮料招商 是由中国保健食品招商网会员发布的改善胃肠类招商信息：<br><p style=\"margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;margin-left:26.985pt;\" class=\"p0\"><span style=\"font-family:\'新宋体\';font-size:12pt;font-weight:bold;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\">本品是猴头菇提取物、姬松茸提取物、天门冬氨酸钙（螯合钙）科学配伍浓缩，精制而成<span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';\">.</span><span style=\"font-family:新宋体;\">。</span></span><span style=\"font-family:\'新宋体\';font-size:12pt;font-weight:bold;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\"></span></p><p style=\"text-align:left;line-height:18pt;margin:0pt -8.925pt 0pt 26.985pt;background:#ffffff;\" class=\"p0\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Arial\';color:#333333;font-size:15pt;font-weight:bold;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\">猴头菇</span><span style=\"font-family:\'Arial\';color:#333333;font-size:12pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\">性平、味甘。利五脏，助消化；具有健胃，补虚，抗癌，益肾精之功效；主治食少便溏、胃及十二指肠溃疡、浅表性胃炎、神经衰弱、食道癌、胃癌、眩晕、阳痿等病症。并对治疗肠癌有辅助作用。年老体弱者食用猴头菇，有滋补强身的作用</span><span style=\"font-family:\'新宋体\';color:#333333;font-size:12pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\">，对青少年厌食及食欲不振、记忆力减退效果显著。</span><span style=\"font-family:\'Arial\';color:#000000;font-size:12pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\">是我国著名的八大<span style=\"font-family:Arial;\">“</span><span style=\"font-family:新宋体;\">山珍</span><span style=\"font-family:Arial;\">”</span><span style=\"font-family:新宋体;\">之一，且与海参、熊掌、燕窝并称为</span></span><span style=\"font-family:\'新宋体\';color:#000000;font-size:12pt;text-decoration:underline;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\">中国四大名菜</span><span style=\"font-family:\'Arial\';color:#000000;font-size:12pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\">，在封建社会，只有皇室御厨和权贵之家方能享用。</span><span style=\"font-family:\'新宋体\';color:#333333;font-size:12pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\"></span></p><p style=\"text-align:left;line-height:18pt;text-indent:23.88pt;margin:0pt -8.925pt 0pt -23.88pt;background:#ffffff;\" class=\"p0\"><span style=\"font-family:\'宋体\';font-size:12pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\">猴头菇</span><span style=\"font-family:\'新宋体\';font-size:12pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\">提取物的十一大功效：一．控制肿瘤生长。&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">1.</span><span style=\"font-family:新宋体;\">控制肿瘤细胞核酸的合成。&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">2.</span><span style=\"font-family:新宋体;\">对瘤细胞生长有直接控制作用。二</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">.&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family:新宋体;\">提高和调节免疫功能。三</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">.</span><span style=\"font-family:新宋体;\">促进肠运动、增加胃动力，</span></span><span style=\"font-family:\'新宋体\';font-size:12pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\"></span></p><p style=\"text-align:left;line-height:18pt;margin:0pt -8.925pt 0pt 26.985pt;background:#ffffff;\" class=\"p0\"><span style=\"font-family:\'新宋体\';font-size:12pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\">四<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">.&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family:新宋体;\">促进消化道溃疡和炎症的修复。五</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">.</span><span style=\"font-family:新宋体;\">控制幽门螺旋杆菌（</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">HP)</span><span style=\"font-family:新宋体;\">生长，保护胃上皮细胞免受</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">HP</span><span style=\"font-family:新宋体;\">的伤害。六</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">.</span><span style=\"font-family:新宋体;\">抗辐射。七</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">.</span><span style=\"font-family:新宋体;\">抗疲劳，八</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">.</span><span style=\"font-family:新宋体;\">提高生存能力。九</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">.</span><span style=\"font-family:新宋体;\">改善血液循环。十</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">.</span><span style=\"font-family:新宋体;\">改善胚胎营养状态和提高脑容量。十一</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">.</span><span style=\"font-family:新宋体;\">抗衰老防止智力衰退、神经衰弱，植物神经衰退和早老性痴呆，</span></span><span style=\"font-family:\'新宋体\';color:#333333;font-size:12pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\"></span></p><p style=\"text-align:left;line-height:18pt;text-indent:24pt;margin:0pt -8.925pt 0pt -24pt;background:#ffffff;\" class=\"p0\"><span style=\"font-family:\'新宋体\';background:#ffffff;color:#333333;font-size:12pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-shading:#ffffff;\">临床广泛应用于胃癌、食道癌、喷门癌、肠癌的治疗，效果显著，且无不良反应。据统计，用猴头制剂治疗<span style=\"font-family:Tahoma;\">134</span><span style=\"font-family:新宋体;\">例胃癌，总有效率为</span><span style=\"font-family:Tahoma;\">78.5%</span><span style=\"font-family:新宋体;\">。上海肿瘤医院治疗上消化道</span><span style=\"font-family:Tahoma;\">166</span><span style=\"font-family:新宋体;\">例癌症，经病理细胞学证实或</span><span style=\"font-family:Tahoma;\">X</span><span style=\"font-family:新宋体;\">线诊断，且患者以中晚期偏多，或已有淋巴结与远处脏器转移，总有效率为</span><span style=\"font-family:Tahoma;\">69.3%</span><span style=\"font-family:新宋体;\">。猴头菇多糖对慢性萎缩性胃炎、慢性浅表性胃炎、胃窦炎等均有明显的治疗作用，对胃痛、胃胀、嗳气、泛酸大便隐血、食欲不振等症有良好的缓解作用。猴头菇所含有不饱和脂肪酸，可促进血液循环，能降低血液中的胆固醇含量，是高血压病、心脑血管疾病患者的理想食品。猴头菇多糖还是有效的免疫增强剂，手术后及癌症化疗后的病人宜经常食用，可增加免疫力。总之，猴头菇堪称降服癌症的克星，在国内外市场上享有盛誉。</span></span><span style=\"font-family:\'新宋体\';color:#333333;font-size:12pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\"></span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\" class=\"p0\"><span style=\"font-family:\'新宋体\';background:#ffffff;color:#333333;font-size:12pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-shading:#ffffff;\">——摘自中国医药科技出版社《绿色食用菌与保健&nbsp;》</span></p><span style=\"font-family:\'新宋体\';background:#ffffff;color:#333333;font-size:12pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-shading:#ffffff;\"> <p style=\"margin-top:0pt;text-indent:28.8pt;margin-bottom:0pt;margin-left:-28.8pt;\" class=\"p0\"><span style=\"font-family:\'宋体\';font-size:15pt;font-weight:bold;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\">姬松茸</span><span style=\"font-family:\'宋体\';font-size:15pt;font-weight:bold;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\"></span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0pt;text-indent:18pt;margin-bottom:0pt;margin-left:-18pt;\" class=\"p0\"><span style=\"font-family:\'宋体\';font-size:12pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\">&nbsp;姬松茸是一种营养成份十分丰富的食用菌，干菇蛋白含量高达<span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';\">43.19%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">，糖类含量</span><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';\">41.56%&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">，氨基酸含量达干重的</span><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';\">19.22%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">，其中有促进儿童生长发育作用的赖氨酸、精氨酸，含量高达氨基酸总量的</span><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';\">39.7%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">，</span></span><span style=\"font-family:\'宋体\';font-size:12pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\"></span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0pt;text-indent:30.84pt;margin-bottom:0pt;margin-left:-30.84pt;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1;\" class=\"p0\"><span style=\"font-family:\'宋体\';font-size:12pt;\"><span style=\"mso-list:Ignore;\">一、</span></span><span style=\"font-family:\'宋体\';font-size:12pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\">姬松茸的药理作用</span><span style=\"font-family:\'宋体\';font-size:12pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\"></span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;margin-left:26.985pt;\" class=\"p0\"><span style=\"font-family:\'宋体\';font-size:12pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;姬松茸有良好的抗肿瘤效果，日本三重大学医学部，冈本大学等将多形细胞肉瘤（非上皮癌恶性肿瘤细胞）接种到小白鼠体内，<span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';\">24</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">小时后确认该肿瘤接种存活。然后分别用姬松茸、香菇、云芝、灵芝、滑菇等十五种食用菌多糖喂食，姬松茸多糖每天喂食</span><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';\">10</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">毫克，其他十四种食用菌多糖每天喂食</span><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';\">30</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">毫克。</span><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';\">10</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">天后小鼠的生存率：姬松茸为</span><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';\">90.1%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">，而其他食用菌为</span><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';\">20%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">—</span><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';\">90%&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">。然后这些存活的小白鼠用多形细胞肉瘤癌细胞再次接种，小白鼠存活率：姬松茸为</span><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';\">99.4%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">，其他各种食用菌分别为，</span><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';\">77.8%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">—</span><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';\">98.5%&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">。该实验数据已被日本国立癌症中心研究所、东京大学医学部、东京医药大学所证实。</span></span><span style=\"font-family:\'宋体\';font-size:12pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\"></span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0pt;text-indent:30.84pt;margin-bottom:0pt;margin-left:-30.84pt;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1;\" class=\"p0\"><span style=\"font-family:\'宋体\';font-size:12pt;\"><span style=\"mso-list:Ignore;\">二、</span></span><span style=\"font-family:\'宋体\';font-size:12pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\">姬松茸人体有哪些作用</span><span style=\"font-family:\'宋体\';font-size:12pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\"></span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0pt;text-indent:24pt;margin-bottom:0pt;margin-left:-24pt;\" class=\"p0\"><span style=\"font-family:\'宋体\';font-size:12pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\">姬松茸有调节血压是高血压病人血压降低，低血压病人血压升高及降血粘稠作用。对冠心病、心肌梗塞、动脉硬化、末梢血管萎缩症、重症肺炎、败血病、白血病、恶性淋巴肿瘤等病有改善症状的功效。姬松茸对胃、十二指肠溃疡，各种慢性胃炎，慢性口腔炎乙型肝炎，肝硬化，便秘、食欲减退，肾功能衰竭等疾病有治疗作用。姬松茸还能抗过敏、消浮肿、改善自主神经失调症状的功效。</span><span style=\"font-family:\'宋体\';font-size:12pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\"></span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\" class=\"p0\"><span style=\"font-family:\'新宋体\';background:#ffffff;color:#333333;font-size:12pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-shading:#ffffff;\">——摘自中国医药科技出版社《绿色食用菌与保健</span></p></span><br>符合宝力康生物有限公司代理商要求的客户可以直接留言与厂家联系。');
